        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "4CcOX",
          "name": "s2body",
          "fill": "#374151",
          "content": "- Nav links: Hover underline (2px, ease-out 200ms), active state bold\n- Search bar: Click to expand/focus, show recent searches dropdown\n- Cart icon: Badge count (red dot) when items in cart\n- User icon: Click opens dropdown (Login/Register/My Account)\n- Logo: Click navigates to homepage\n- Sticky: Navbar becomes sticky on scroll (add subtle shadow on stick)",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "RcN07",
