          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "HywQv",
          "name": "s3body",
          "fill": "#374151",
          "content": "- Tag pill 'NEW SEASON': Subtle pulse animation on load (scale 1.0-1.02, 2s loop)\n- 'Shop Now' button: Hover bg darken to #5228C9, scale 1.02 (200ms ease-out)\n- 'Sell With Us' button: Hover bg #F0EAFF, text stays #6432FC (200ms)\n- Hero image: Gentle parallax on scroll (0.1 factor)\n- Entry animation: Title slides up + fade (400ms), desc follows (500ms), buttons (600ms)",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
