          "id": "jnJ2l",
          "name": "s4b",
          "fill": "#374151",
          "content": "- Category circles: Hover scale 1.05 + shadow elevation (300ms ease-out)\n- Click: Navigate to /category/{slug}\n- Label: Hover text color #6432FC (200ms)\n- Entry: Stagger fade-in from left, 80ms delay per item",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
