          "content": "- Brand card hover: Border color #6432FC, bg #F8F5FF (200ms ease-out)\n- Click: Navigate to /brand/{slug}\n- [DEV NOTE] Consider adding brand logo images in future iteration\n- Entry: Stagger fade-in, 60ms delay per card",
