          "content": "- Links: Hover color #FFFFFF from #9CA3AF (200ms)\n- Social icons: Hover scale 1.1 + color #6432FC (200ms)\n- Logo: Click navigates to homepage\n- Newsletter input (if added): Focus border #6432FC\n- Legal links: Open in new tab (_blank)",
