        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "SDE9s",
          "name": "s10b",
          "fill": "#374151",
          "content": "- Scroll: Smooth scroll behavior (scroll-behavior: smooth)\n- Back to top: Show floating button after scrolling 600px (fade-in 200ms)\n- Page transitions: Fade crossfade between pages (300ms)\n- Loading: Skeleton screens for product cards and images\n- Responsive: This design is 1440px desktop; H5 adaptation pending\n- Reduced motion: Respect prefers-reduced-motion, disable parallax and loops\n- All animations use ease-out-quart easing unless noted otherwise\n- Touch targets: Minimum 44x44px for all interactive elements",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
